<!-- '''B. Jayant Baliga''' is an Indian [[electrical_engineer|electrical engineer]] best known for his work in power semiconductor devices, and particularly invention of the [[insulated_gate_bipolar_transistor|insulated gate bipolar transistor]]. Scientific American magazine included him among the 'Eight Heroes of the Semiconductor Revolution' when commemorating the 50th anniversary of the invention of the transistor.<ref>[http://www.ece.ncsu.edu/people.php/bjbaliga Dr. Jayant Baliga - Primary Faculty - Department of Electrical and Computer Engineering]</ref> -->
'''B·賈揚特·巴利加'''（{{lang-en|'''B. Jayant Baliga'''}}，{{bd|1948年|4月28日|||catIdx=B. Jayant Baliga}}<ref>{{cite web|title=B. Jayant Baliga: Designing The Insulated-Gate Bipolar Transistor|url=http://electronicdesign.com/analog/b-jayant-baliga-designing-insulated-gate-bipolar-transistor|author=John Edwards|publisher=Electronic Design|date=Nov 22, 2010|accessdate=2014-05-15|language=en|archive-date=2014-05-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140517120920/http://electronicdesign.com/analog/b-jayant-baliga-designing-insulated-gate-bipolar-transistor|dead-url=no}}</ref>），印度[[電機工程師|電機工程師]]，專精於功率半導體元件，發明了[[絕緣柵雙極電晶體|絕緣柵雙極電晶體]]。為紀念電晶體發明50周年，[[科學美國人|科學美國人]]雜誌將其列為「八位半導體革命英雄」（{{lang|en|Eight Heroes of the Semiconductor Revolution}}）之一<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ece.ncsu.edu/people.php/bjbaliga|title=Dr. Jayant Baliga|accessdate=2014-05-15|publisher=North Carolina State University|language=en|archive-date=2014-05-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140517152944/http://www.ece.ncsu.edu/people.php/bjbaliga|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==背景==
<!-- Baliga grew up in a small village called Jalahalli near [[Bangalore|Bangalore]], [[India|India]]. His father is a former head of Bharat Electronics Limited.<ref name=forbes>[http://ibnlive.in.com/news/jayant-baligas-invention-is-a-power-saver/234168-55.html Jayant Baliga's invention is a power saver], Shishir Prasad, Forbes India, Feb 27, 2012</ref> He received his B.Tech in Electrical Engineering from the [[Indian_Institute_of_Technology,_Madras|Indian Institute of Technology, Madras]], in 1969, and his MS (1971) and PhD (1974) in Electrical Engineering from the [[Rensselaer_Polytechnic_Institute|Rensselaer Polytechnic Institute]]. -->

巴利加出生在[[印度|印度]][[清奈|馬德拉斯]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://connection.ebscohost.com/c/articles/57311354/designing-insulated-gate-bipolar-transistor|title=Designing The Insulated-Gate Bipolar Transistor|accessdate=2014-05-15|language=en|archive-date=2014-05-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140517115841/http://connection.ebscohost.com/c/articles/57311354/designing-insulated-gate-bipolar-transistor|dead-url=no}}</ref>，成長於印度[[班加羅爾|班加羅爾]]附近的小村莊{{tsl|en|Jalahalli|加拉哈立}}。父親是巴拉特電子有限公司（{{lang|en|Bharat Electronics Limited}}）的前任負責人<ref name=forbes>{{cite web|url=http://ibnlive.in.com/news/jayant-baligas-invention-is-a-power-saver/234168-55.html|title=Jayant Baliga's invention is a power saver|author=Shishir Prasad|publisher=Forbes India|date=Feb 27, 2012|accessdate=2014-05-15|language=en|archive-date=2014-05-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140518020931/http://ibnlive.in.com/news/jayant-baligas-invention-is-a-power-saver/234168-55.html|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。於1969年取得{{tsl|en|Indian Institute of Technology Madras|印度理工學院馬德拉斯校區}}的學士學位，並分別於1971年及1974年取得[[壬色列理工學院|壬色列理工學院]]的碩士與博士學位。

==職業生涯==
<!-- He worked 15 years at the [[General_Electric|General Electric]] Research and Development Center in [[Schenectady,_New_York|Schenectady, New York]], then joined [[North_Carolina_State_University|North Carolina State University]] in 1988 as a Full Professor. He was promoted to Distinguished University Professor in 1997.<ref name=forbes/> His invention [[insulated_gate_bipolar_transistor|insulated gate bipolar transistor]] that combines sciences from two streams Electronics engineering and Electrical engineering. This has resulted in cost savings of over $15 trillion for consumers, and is forming a basis for smart grid.<ref name=forbes/> Baliga then worked in academic field. He also founded three companies that made products based on semiconductor technologies.<ref name=forbes/> -->

巴利加在[[紐約州|紐約州]][[斯克內克塔迪_(紐約州)|斯克內克塔迪]]通用電氣公司研究發展中心工作達15年<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ieeeghn.org/wiki/index.php/B._Jayant_Baliga|title=B. Jayant Baliga|publisher=IEEE|accessdate=2014-05-16|language=en|archive-date=2014-05-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140517120755/http://www.ieeeghn.org/wiki/index.php/B._Jayant_Baliga|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，後於1988年時擔任[[北卡羅來納州立大學|北卡羅來納州立大學]]全職教授。1997年時，獲選為傑出大學教授（{{lang|en|Distinguished University Professor}}）<ref name=forbes/>。巴利加所發明的[[絕緣柵雙極電晶體|絕緣柵雙極電晶體]]，結合了電子工程及電機工程兩大科學領域。此項發明為消費者節省的金錢超過美金15兆，同時形成智能電網的基礎<ref name=forbes/>。巴利加不僅工作於學術領域，同時也是三家利用半導體技術製造產品公司的創辦人<ref name=forbes/>。且擁有的美國專利超過100項。2010年，獲美國總統[[歐巴馬|歐巴馬]]頒贈代表美國工程師最高榮譽的{{tsl|en|National Medal of Technology and Innovation|美國國家技術與創新獎章}}<ref name=WhiteHousePressRelease/>。並於2014年因「功率半導體元件的發明、改良及商業化對社會的巨大貢獻」獲頒[[IEEE榮譽獎章|IEEE榮譽獎章]]<ref name="#1">{{cite web|title=IEEE 2014 Medals and Awards Recipients|url=http://theinstitute.ieee.org/people/achievements/recipients-of-the-2014-medals-and-awards|publisher=[[IEEE|IEEE]]|accessdate=2014-02-14|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140224000716/http://theinstitute.ieee.org/people/achievements/recipients-of-the-2014-medals-and-awards|archivedate=2014-02-24}}</ref>。

